Jazz Jackrabbit 2 Multigames/Minigames map.
===========================================

V. 1.0 Pre-Final

Do you know Jazz Jackrabbit 2, one of the best platformer of 1998? Here you can get minigames map inspired by them!

Map has 17 minigames.

This is my first minigames map. Feel free to comment it. :-)

Some ideas for minimaps are taken from: mg_hellz_multigame and mg_pauls_multigames.


Support Jazz Jackrabbit 2 community and learn more about JJ2! Visit:
http://www.jazz2online.com/
http://www.jazzjackrabbit.net/


Map by: nkpkiller / 2012 , POLAND


All rights reserved to Epic Games for making Jazz Jackrabbit 2.


Download size note:

- Map uncompressed size - 74MB
- Compressed with Zip [Gamebanana download] size: 41MB
- Compressed with Bzip2 [FastDownload in CSS] size: 39MB
